Rating: 1
1 hour 10 min at 450 deg is way too long for this recipe. My onions were burned to a crisp and the potatoes had a bitter note. My box of Lipton Onion Soup had a similar recipe right on the box and it recommended cooking for 35 min at 425. I might try the rcipe again according to those instructions.

