Rating: 3
Decidedly simple and quite good. I have made two changes. First I've added 2 cloves of finely chopped garlic (more if you like the the herb), to the mix, Toss, let stand about 2 to 5 minutes, toss again, then procede. Secondly, I fully line my baking dish with aluminum foil... clean-up is absolutely simple by doing this.